syntaxExplanation:
Here is the core syntax for If Else Branching:

```java
// Java implementation for If Else Branching
public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        System.out.println("Executing Java process for: If Else Branching");
        int result = calculateScore(85, 92);
        System.out.println("Final Score: " + result);
    }

    public static int calculateScore(int a, int b) {
        return (a + b) / 2;
    }
}
```

